<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>mermaid on 木瓜有点甜</title><link>https://jimugou.com/tags/mermaid/</link><description>Recent content in mermaid on 木瓜有点甜</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 Jul 2022 20:46:15 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://jimugou.com/tags/mermaid/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Mermaid书写范例实例</title><link>https://jimugou.com/notes/2022/08/29/223909/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Jul 2022 20:46:15 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jimugou.com/notes/2022/08/29/223909/</guid><description>&lt;p>依赖 mermaid 支持，&lt;strong>遵循语法进行书写可实现渲染出图&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="流程图">流程图&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>关键字
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>flowchart&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>方向
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>TB(top to bottom)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>BT(bottom to top)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>LR(left to right)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>RL(right to left)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Mermaid 语句的结束，有两种方式:&lt;strong>在结尾加分号&lt;/strong>；&lt;strong>换行&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> a--&amp;gt;b
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> c--&amp;gt;d
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> a--&amp;gt;b
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> c--&amp;gt;d
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="连线">连线&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="线种类">线种类&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A---实线; %% AB之间，以一条实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.-虚线; %% AB之间，以一条虚线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A===粗实线; %% AB之间，以一条粗实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A--&amp;gt;箭头实线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.-&amp;gt;箭头虚线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头虚线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A==&amp;gt;箭头粗实线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头粗实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A~~~不可见 %%可用于节点定位
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A---实线; %% AB之间，以一条实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.-虚线; %% AB之间，以一条虚线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A===粗实线; %% AB之间，以一条粗实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A--&amp;gt;箭头实线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.-&amp;gt;箭头虚线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头虚线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A==&amp;gt;箭头粗实线; %% AB之间，以一条箭头粗实线连接
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart RL
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 反向实线箭头--&amp;gt;A; %% 这是一条从B到A的反向实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart RL
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 反向实线箭头--&amp;gt;A; %% 这是一条从B到A的反向实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="箭头类型">箭头类型&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">9
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A --o 实线o; %% 实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A --x 实线x; %% 实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A -.-o 虚线o; %% 虚线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A -.-x 虚线x; %% 虚线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A ==o 粗实线o; %% 粗实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A ==x 粗实线x; %% 粗实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">%% 使用flowchart关键字
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A --o 实线o; %% 实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A --x 实线x; %% 实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A -.-o 虚线o; %% 虚线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A -.-x 虚线x; %% 虚线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A ==o 粗实线o; %% 粗实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A ==x 粗实线x; %% 粗实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="多向箭头">多向箭头&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>有三种: 使用首尾相同的 o 或 x，或者一对 &amp;lt; &amp;gt;; 不能使用 o&amp;ndash;x 这样首尾不同的&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 实线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A o--o B; %% 多向实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> C &amp;lt;--&amp;gt; D; %% 多向实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> E x--x F; %% 多向实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 虚线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> G o-.-o H; %% 多向虚线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> I &amp;lt;-.-&amp;gt; J; %% 多向虚线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> K x-.-x L; %% 多向虚线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 粗实线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> M o==o N; %% 多向粗实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> O &amp;lt;==&amp;gt; P; %% 多向粗实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> R x==x S; %% 多向粗实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 实线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A o--o B; %% 多向实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> C &amp;lt;--&amp;gt; D; %% 多向实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> E x--x F; %% 多向实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 虚线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> G o-.-o H; %% 多向虚线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> I &amp;lt;-.-&amp;gt; J; %% 多向虚线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> K x-.-x L; %% 多向虚线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> %% 粗实线
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> M o==o N; %% 多向粗实线o
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> O &amp;lt;==&amp;gt; P; %% 多向粗实线箭头
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> R x==x S; %% 多向粗实线x
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="连线文本">连线文本&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="嵌入式">嵌入式&lt;/h4>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A--嵌入式:实线间的文本--&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以实线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.嵌入式:虚线间的文本.-&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以虚线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A==嵌入式:粗实线间的文本==&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以粗实线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A--嵌入式:实线间的文本--&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以实线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.嵌入式:虚线间的文本.-&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以虚线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A==嵌入式:粗实线间的文本==&amp;gt;B; %% AB之间以粗实线连接，且有一段连线文本
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="外部式">外部式&lt;/h4>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">```mermaid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">&lt;/span>flowchart LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A--&amp;gt;|实线间文本|B;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A-.-&amp;gt;|虚线间文本|B;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A==&amp;gt;|粗实线间文本|B;
